Package com.g1.mychess.player.dto

Class PlayerProfileUpdateDTO

java.lang.Object
com.g1.mychess.player.dto.PlayerProfileUpdateDTO
public class PlayerProfileUpdateDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) class that represents a player's profile update information. This class is used for updating a player's profile details such as their full name, bio, avatar URL, location (country, region, city), and the visibility of the profile.
